      "writtenOn": "2019-03-21T23:00:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "In this case based on simplicity of the generator implementation. luci.notifer nodes are \"terminal\" (either leafs or root depending on chosen direction), and can\u0027t be part of a cycle, so it doesn\u0027t really matter what direction it used.\n\nThis direction is simpler, since it allows to use builder_ref.follow(...) function to disambiguate references to builders specified without bucket name.",
